<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA621_11_SU_0007_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema621_11.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema621_11_su_0007">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-type="1" data-text="자기주도 3">
          <span class="blue line" lang="y">내 힘으로 풀어요</span>
          <span lang="y">공부한 내용을 확인해요</span>
        </h2>
      </section>
      <section class="title type2 jgjd_3_sub_title">
        <h2 data-head="6" class="is_star" lang="y">
          <div class="fraction_row">
            <div class="fraction_inn">
              가로가 <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>5</span></span
              >m이고 세로가 <span class="fraction_box"><span>7</span><span>10</span></span
              >m인 직사각형 모양의 담장을 칠하는 데 페인트 <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>3</span></span
              >L를 사용했습니다. 담장 1 ㎡를 칠하는 데 필요한
            </div>
            페인트는 몇 L인지 구하려고 합니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <div class="input_area">
          <article class="page page_1">
            <h3 lang="y">직사각형 모양 담장의 넓이는 몇 ㎡ 인지 구해 보세요.</h3>
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <div class="col1">
                <span class="tag" lang="y">식</span>
                <div class="col_inn f32b">
                  <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="(4)/(5)&times;(7)/(10)"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  =
                  <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="(14)/(25)"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col2">
                <span class="tag" lang="y">답</span>
                <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="(14)/(25)"></math-field>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="page page_2">
            <h3 lang="y">담장 1 ㎡를 칠하는 데 필요한 페인트는 몇 L인지 구해 보세요.</h3>
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <div class="col1">
                <span class="tag" lang="y">식</span>
                <div class="col_inn f32b">
                  <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="(2)/(3)÷(14)/(25)"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  =
                  <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="1(4)/(21)" data-answer-multi='{"values": ["1(4)/(21)", "(25)/(21)"]}' data-multi-hint="y"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col2">
                <span class="tag" lang="y">답</span>
                <div class="col_inn">
                  <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="1(4)/(21)" data-answer-multi='{"values": ["1(4)/(21)", "(25)/(21)"]}' data-multi-hint="y"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <span class="f32b">L</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
